{"title_page": "Topik Petang (TV program)", "text_new": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{Orphan|date=April 2020}}\n{{unreferenced|date=August 2015}}\n}}\n\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name            = Topik Petang\n| image                =\n| caption              =\n| show_name_2          =\n| genre                = [[News program]]\n| creator              = \n| director             =\n| developer            =\n| presenter            = Limystina Novatra{{br}}Melisa Gandasari{{br}}Tika Ghaffar{{br}}Deba Depari{{br}}Aprilia Yahya{{br}}Arif Kurniawan{{br}}Ziza Hamzah\n| starring             =\n| voices               =\n| narrated             =\n| theme_music_composer =\n| opentheme            =\n| endtheme             =\n| composer             =\n| country              = Indonesia\n| language             = [[Indonesian language|Indonesian]]\n| num_seasons          =\n| num_episodes         =\n| list_episodes        =\n| executive_producer   =\n| producer             = [[antv]]\n| supervising_producer =\n| asst_producer        =\n| co-producer          =\n| editor               =\n| story_editor         =\n| location             = [[Jakarta]]\n| camera               = [[Multi-camera]]\n| runtime              = 30 minutes\n| network              = [[antv]]\n| picture_format       = [[PAL]]\n| audio_format         =\n| first_run            = \n| first_aired          = April 30, 2006\n| last_aired           = October 16, 2013\n| preceded_by          =\n| followed_by          =\n| related              =\n| website              = http://www.an.tv\n}}\n\n'''Topik Petang''' is an Indonesian television [[news]] program, which was broadcast Monday to Friday at 18:30, Saturday and Sunday at 17:30, on [[antv]]. It debuted on April 30, 2006. The program was broadcast at different times on [[antv]] if the broadcast of a sporting event interferes with the program's usual scheduling. ''Topik Petang'' last aired on October 16, 2013.\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.an.tv/berita an.tv]\n\n[